      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a prime example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the 4.0L S65 V8 engine with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution and mechanical grip. The chassis maintains its structural integrity, providing the communicative feedback expected of the M-division's longitudinal subframe architecture. Essential preventative maintenance, including throttle actuators and rod bearing service, has been addressed to ensure the valvetrain and VANOS system perform at peak efficiency. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car optimized for visceral engagement.",
